# Tailwind CSS v4.0.0 - Official Rules

> Source: https://tailwindcss.com/docs
> Last fetched: 2026-02-05

## ABSOLUTE PROHIBITIONS (ZERO TOLERANCE)

### Universal
- NO placeholders: `TODO`, `FIXME`, `XXX`, `HACK`, `...`
- NO hardcoded colors - use design tokens (`ocean-deep`, `ocean-glow`, etc.)
- NO magic numbers for spacing - use Tailwind scale

### Tailwind Specific
- NO inline styles (`style={{...}}`) - use Tailwind utilities
- NO custom CSS unless absolutely necessary
- NO `!important` overrides
- NO hardcoded pixel values - use Tailwind spacing scale
- NO color values outside the design system
- NO z-index values outside defined scale

## REQUIRED Patterns

### Mobile-First Responsive Design

```tsx
// CORRECT: Mobile-first approach
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4">
  {items.map(item => (
    <Card key={item.id} />
  ))}
</div>

// WRONG: Desktop-first
<div className="grid grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-1"> {/* Wrong order! */}
```

### Breakpoint System

| Breakpoint | Min Width | Usage |
|------------|-----------|-------|
| `sm:` | 640px | Small tablets |
| `md:` | 768px | Tablets |
| `lg:` | 1024px | Laptops |
| `xl:` | 1280px | Desktops |
| `2xl:` | 1536px | Large screens |

```tsx
// Responsive text sizing
<h1 className="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
  Title
</h1>

// Responsive padding
<section className="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  Content
</section>
```

### Dark Mode Support

```tsx
// Dark mode with class strategy
<div className="bg-white dark:bg-ocean-abyss text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
  <button className="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-blue-600">
    Click me
  </button>
</div>

// Complex dark mode combinations
<button className="dark:lg:hover:bg-indigo-600">
  Dark mode + large screen + hover
</button>
```

### Project Design Tokens

Use the custom ocean-themed color palette defined in `tailwind.config.ts`:

```tsx
// Custom project colors
<div className="bg-ocean-surface">    {/* Light surface */}
<div className="bg-ocean-shallow">    {/* Shallow water */}
<div className="bg-ocean-medium">     {/* Medium depth */}
<div className="bg-ocean-deep">       {/* Deep ocean */}
<div className="bg-ocean-abyss">      {/* Darkest */}
<div className="text-ocean-glow">     {/* Accent/glow */}
```

### Custom Animations

```tsx
// Use project animations
<div className="animate-float">        {/* Floating effect */}
<div className="animate-bubble">       {/* Bubble rising */}
<div className="animate-light-ray">    {/* Light ray effect */}
```

### Component Styling Pattern

```tsx
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'

interface CardProps {
  className?: string
  variant?: 'default' | 'outlined' | 'elevated'
}

export function Card({ className, variant = 'default' }: CardProps) {
  return (
    <div className={cn(
      // Base styles
      'rounded-lg p-4',
      // Variant styles
      variant === 'default' && 'bg-white dark:bg-ocean-deep',
      variant === 'outlined' && 'border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700',
      variant === 'elevated' && 'shadow-lg',
      // Allow overrides
      className
    )}>
      {children}
    </div>
  )
}
```

## FORBIDDEN Patterns

### Wrong: Inline styles
```tsx
// WRONG
<div style={{ padding: '16px', marginTop: '20px' }}>

// CORRECT
<div className="p-4 mt-5">
```

### Wrong: Hardcoded colors
```tsx
// WRONG
<div className="bg-[#1a365d]">

// CORRECT
<div className="bg-ocean-deep">
```

### Wrong: Desktop-first responsive
```tsx
// WRONG
<div className="hidden sm:block md:hidden lg:block">

// CORRECT - Mobile first
<div className="block sm:hidden md:block lg:hidden">
```

### Wrong: Using px values
```tsx
// WRONG
<div className="p-[17px] mt-[23px]">

// CORRECT - Use spacing scale
<div className="p-4 mt-6">
```

## Spacing Scale Reference

| Class | Size |
|-------|------|
| `p-1` | 0.25rem (4px) |
| `p-2` | 0.5rem (8px) |
| `p-3` | 0.75rem (12px) |
| `p-4` | 1rem (16px) |
| `p-5` | 1.25rem (20px) |
| `p-6` | 1.5rem (24px) |
| `p-8` | 2rem (32px) |
| `p-10` | 2.5rem (40px) |
| `p-12` | 3rem (48px) |

## Flexbox & Grid Patterns

```tsx
// Centered container
<div className="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">

// Responsive grid
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

// Sidebar layout
<div className="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
  <aside className="w-full lg:w-64 shrink-0" />
  <main className="flex-1" />
</div>
```

## Hover, Focus & State Modifiers

```tsx
<button className="
  bg-blue-500 
  hover:bg-blue-600 
  focus:ring-2 
  focus:ring-blue-500 
  focus:ring-offset-2
  active:bg-blue-700
  disabled:opacity-50 
  disabled:cursor-not-allowed
  transition-colors
">
  Button
</button>
```

